data.description: Welcome to 1425 East Road, first time on the Market, EVER! This could be your ONCE IN A LIFETIME Opportunity! Single level custom built property available at the perfect time in La Habra Heights. The property has been meticulously cared for by the family who are the original owners.   This is a beautiful Spanish-style home featuring clay tile roof, arched doorways, palladium windows, built in cabinets. 4 bedroom and 3 bath, 2151 sq ft home situated on a 1.11 acre parcel. As you enter the home you get the feeling the home is warm and comfortable steps leading to the living room and family room. Additionally you will find a wet bar/nook in the living area for friends and family to gather & entertain. The kitchen features wood flooring, lots of extra storage & counter space. The Interior has been freshly painted, newer A/C, The primary room is oversized with an ensuite attached featuring a spa tub and huge walk in closet. Outside, you'll find a large lot an above ground spa, covered patio area to dine alfresco surrounded by numerous fruit trees, a garden setting with plants, flowers. Just right for the garden enthusiast. French doors open to plenty of space for outdoor entertaining. The yard is gently sloped and terraced.  Views from the top of the lot. An attached 3 car garage with direct access. Offers additional storage and convenience, parking that may accommodate additional vehicles, RV or boat. Circular driveway, additional parking pad and covered area. Hurry to see this one. La Habra Heights at its best!
